# FixtureGlyph

## Summary

An SVG glyph for a floor-plan fixture, chosen by `@kind`: plant, tree, balloon, stage, red-carpet, dance-floor, arch, projector, cake, bar, curved-wall, rect-decor, round-decor, or circle-cluster, with a dashed placeholder box for unknown kinds. `@color` tints the drawing and `@pattern` ('solid' | 'outline' | 'soft') controls the fill — outline removes it, soft renders it at 45% opacity. Strokes use `vector-effect: non-scaling-stroke`, so line weight stays crisp whether it is stretched across the canvas, shrunk into LayoutPreview, or shown as a picker swatch.

## Import

```js
import FixtureGlyph from '../components/fixture-glyph';
```

## Template Usage

```gjs
<FixtureGlyph
  @kind={{f.kind}}
  @color={{f.color}}
  @pattern={{f.pattern}}
/>
```
